settings.description: Honestly loosely based on one level from the SMBX game 'the invasion 2', for remember a level with the hammer bros themes and mario bros elements? well... here I'm trying to go for that theme!
Luigi finds something wrong at this level and that is that when he knows that it is kaizo, he does everything he has learned in practice
Some neighbors are going to cut off my power and it will take a lot of days to come back, I did nothing they are protesting.
semi-redo of a very old level perhaps. same theme, different layout ya know? though this time I went a bit overboard on them there tilting platforms instead!
Fun Fact: I'm terrible at making underwater levels, so I just decided to take out the water in the underwater, thus creating an... under level.
Mario finds a cave after all but he gets trapped and doesn't know how to escape
I was doing good at first but I gave up...
so many red hot piranha plants! clearly, this dungeon of pipes is out to just roast you, so stay on your toes and don't get burned or biten!
what's up with all these spinning spiny shells? well... be glad ya aren't playing the NES and SNES version here, for ya can't stomp them in them versions of SMB3, but here? you can!
This levels will be shorter but some hard to collect the special coins,and obviously the spike tops are fluttering, it is not a bug obviously HEHE.
Thwomps and Thwimps! this place is full to the brim with these mad rocky foes! think you can make it out of these ruins without getting crushed?
